Texnik topshiriq

Simple Banking System (In-Memory)

1. User entity

-   id (Long): todo Avtomatik generatsiya qilinadigan unikal identifikator.
-   username (String): Mijoz nomi. Takrorlanmas bo‘lishi shart.
-   email (String): pochta manzili.
-   isCorparate (boolean) : comparative major

2. Account entity

-   id (Long): Avtomatik generatsiya qilinadi.
-   userId (Long): Hisob egasining identifikatori.
-   balance : Hisobdagi pul miqdori.
-   Boshlang‘ich qiymat: 0.00.

-   Transaction entity
	fieldlarini logikadan kelib chiqib yozish kerak.

todo from,to,amount,commission,status,description(maybe)
commission: simple <-> simple && corporate <-> corporate && simple <-> corporate 1%

3. API

3.1. User API

1.  User yaratish (POST /api/users)
2.  Userni ID bo‘yicha olish (GET /api/users/{id})
3.  Barcha userlarni olish (GET /api/users)

3.2. Account API

4.  Hisob ochish (POST /api/accounts?userId={id})
todo agar major comparative bo'lsa 10 ta account, agar comparative bo'lmasa hisob 5 tadan oshmasligi kerak

5.  Account balansini olish (GET /api/accounts/{id})

3.3. Transaction API

6.  Deposit (POST /api/transactions/deposit)
7.  Withdraw (POST /api/transactions/withdraw)
8.  Transfer (POST /api/transactions/transfer).
todo oddly user dan corporate userga transfer qismida commission hisoblash kerak. Komissiya o'zingiz istalgan ko'rinishda elon qilishingiz mumkin

